WEBVTT

00:01:30.355 --> 00:01:34.206
that by blaming an attack
on a nation-state,

00:01:34.230 --> 00:01:36.911
you are putting regulators at bay --

00:01:36.935 --> 00:01:38.969
at least for a period of time.

00:01:39.837 --> 00:01:44.320
So where is all of this coming from?

00:01:44.997 --> 00:01:50.490
The United Nations estimates
that 80 percent of it

00:01:50.514 --> 00:01:56.284
is from highly organized
and ultrasophisticated criminal gangs.

00:01:57.254 --> 00:01:58.973
To date,

00:01:58.997 --> 00:02:05.597
this represents one of the largest
illegal economies in the world,